  }, {
    "tStartMs": 138990,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of dig into all of these nuances"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 140910,
    "dDurationMs": 2820,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but also talk about the, the\nsort of practical type of work"
